<p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-gray-400 text-sm px-6 mb-4">Envie os testes direto para seu repositório Git ou ferramenta de gestão de testes.</p>
<div class="bg-white border border-slate-200 dark:bg-[#1f2937] dark:border-border-dark rounded-md p-2 w-48 mx-auto text-left shadow-lg opacity-80 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity">
<div class="text-[10px] text-slate-500 dark:text-gray-500 uppercase font-bold mb-1 pl-2">Exportar como:</div>
<div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-xs text-slate-700 dark:text-white p-1 hover:bg-slate-100 dark:hover:bg-white/5 rounded cursor-pointer">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[14px] text-green-400">code</span> BDD (.feature)
                        </div>
<div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-xs text-slate-700 dark:text-white p-1 hover:bg-slate-100 dark:hover:bg-white/5 rounded cursor-pointer">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[14px] text-blue-400">checklist</span> Checklist (Markdown)
                        </div>
<div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-xs text-slate-700 dark:text-white p-1 hover:bg-slate-100 dark:hover:bg-white/5 rounded cursor-pointer">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[14px] text-blue-500">task</span> Jira Test Cases
                        </div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
